  • Classes in com.gridgraph.storage.bulk used by com.gridgraph.storage 
    Class and Description
    IBulkUpdateEdge
    The IBulkUpdateEdge interface should be implemented by any class whose instances are intended to provides bulk update access on a TxEdge.
    Note that this interface is abstracted from BulkUpdateEdge, developed by others before this interface's introduction, please refer to the original class for implementation details.
    IBulkUpdateVertex
    The IBulkUpdateVertex interface should be implemented by any class whose instances are intended to provides bulk update access on a TxVertex.
